<item>
            <title>[PDFBOX-4494] Problem with google noto bold font and hungarian characters </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-4494</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I have generated a PDF with Hungarian characters using both Noto regular and Noto bold fonts.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The texts looks correct in the PDF but when generating the PDF page as an image the bold text misplaces the accent for the Hungarian character.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The image is generated using the following command:&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;java -jar pdfbox-app-2.0.14.jar PDFToImage a.pdf&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Attached are the a.pdf and the generated image.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
